    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-08-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-08-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="61" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d61">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Pacheco</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States in Guatemala and Honduras</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-08-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 10,
                                    1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Pacheco informs the Department that the steamer <hi rend="italic">City of
                            Panama</hi>, being refused clearance papers at La Union on account of
                        refusing to give up political refugees on board, left that place without
                        clearance papers, and, upon reaching Libertad, was detained and declared
                        confiscated.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
